{
  "stem": "27390.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they charged a lot of-- a lot more than what we normally paid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this went on for a few days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then gradually they introduced other-- that we can't walk in the street after-- before 8:00 and after 5:00 in the afternoon Jews were forbidden to walk in the street.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Jews were forbidden to travel by public transport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were not allowed to walk in the-- we lived in the, as I told you before, at [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Vikovska ?] Street, which was the main thoroughfare.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we were not allowed to walk in that street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Jews were not allowed to walk in that street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in order that we-- if we wanted to get out of the apartment, to walk-- not to walk in the street, but to get through the street and to the side streets, we had to buy a permit, a special permit.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For all the people that lived in the street, in that street, had to buy permits.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they charged I think 5 or 10 marks per permit, which was a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you had to have it in order to buy-- to get out into the side streets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this went on far a few weeks like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- every day, they brought in new laws.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jews should have to wear a star of-- a yellow Star of David on the front and in the back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jewish businesses had to put out a notice that they're owned by Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jewish bakers were only allowed to bake bread, not cake or biscuits.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jewish businesses, the big businesses, they sent in the commissars, they were called, officials, to see how the business is run.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
